Development Roadmap
Phase 1: Core Engine
Basic packet capture and rule filtering
Event hashing and local ledger
Command-line dashboard

Phase 2: Blockchain Layer
On-chain anchoring of hashes
Wallet key integration (Ed25519 / ECDSA)
Anchor verification scripts

Phase 3: Consensus + P2P
Multi-node message sync
Gossip-based reputation exchange
Fork resolution for conflicting events

Phase 4: UI & Monitoring
Web dashboard
Prometheus/Grafana metrics
REST API for log queries
